description:
Virtual COM ports for W&T network devices (Com-Server, LAN-Modem)

Connect a Com-Server, a LAN modem or a Web-IO with serial interface to 
the network and establish a virtual COM port on your system to make your 
serial applications network-capable.   
Please note: A currently installed copy of wt-com-pnp will prevent 
wt-com-legacy from being installed and must be explicitly uninstalled 
first.
